title: About Me
text:
Hi! My name is Cara Chang (she/her), and I am a graduating senior at Northwestern University majoring in Data Science, Economics, and International Studies. I am passionate about the intersection of machine learning and business, with experience in computational biology research and a consulting organization, CASE.
